<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>LMS Activation Mail</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      color: #333;
    }

    a {
      color: #0070f3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #0070f3;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #555;
    }

    table td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #0070f3;
      padding: 30px;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 6px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 6px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to E-Learning!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <span style="font-weight: 600;"><%= user.name %></span>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for joining our educational platform, LMS E-Learning. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:
      </p>
      <h2 style="font-size: 32px; color: #0070f3; text-align: center;"><%= activationCode %></h2>
      <p>Please input this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>
        If you haven't registered for an LMS account, kindly disregard this email.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>
        Should you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@lms.com">support@lms.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
